    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >利用这款由 <strong>Pierre “El Tyranos” Azuelos</strong> 设计的全新服装包，为您的《Crusader Kings III》增添更多历史色彩。这个外观添加内容将为 Paradox Interactive 获奖肯定的中世纪战略角色扮演游戏带来西斯拉夫全阶级角色的新装备。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3275760/extras/9d5fad7976180f8aed1b2eb47b50840c.poster.avif?t=1769090655\" width=616 height=296 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3275760/extras/9d5fad7976180f8aed1b2eb47b50840c.webm?t=1769090655\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3275760/extras/9d5fad7976180f8aed1b2eb47b50840c.mp4?t=1769090655\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>本包内含：</strong></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >6 个服装模型</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >1 个新的腿部装备模型</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >15 件头部装备，包含博莱斯瓦夫一世和卡齐米尔三世的王冠</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >2 件额外的战争贵族头部装备 (一顶王冠和一枚纹章)</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >1 把新剑</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >什切尔别茨文物：波兰君主的皇家加冕之剑</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >11 种服装图案和装饰</p></li></ul>",
